      "text": "Nickel Metal Hydride Battery Replacement"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "CONSULT-II contains a nickel metal hydride battery. When replacing the battery obey the following:",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Replace the nickel metal hydride battery with Genuine CONSULT-II battery only. Use of another battery may present a risk of fire or explosion. The battery may present a fire or chemical burn hazard if mistreated. Do not recharge, disassemble of dispose of in fire.\nKeep the battery out of reach of children and discard used battery conforming to the local regulations.",
      "style": "warning"
    }
